posts.name: Mighty Catcher Chinese Zodiac NFT- Captain Claw (Ox)
posts.description: Mighty Catcher is the 1st live-streaming crane game in BSC Gamefi. As a blockchain game with strategic gamefi elements, where you can earn the XPT token through simple daily missions, skilful gameplay and thanksgiving events. Players can play and grab physical prizes and virtual e-voucher items through real-time remote control.
